In May 2012, T.I. revealed he has invested money in a social marketing app called Yopima.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.vibe.com/photo-gallery/ti-hosts-demo-launch-social-app-yopima-new-york|title=T.I. Hosts Demo Launch For New Social App Yopima In New York (Photos)|date=May 30, 2013|access-date=October 6, 2013|first=Desire|last=Thompson}}</ref>

